1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 33 =

20
00:01:33,380 --> 00:01:36,620
= The Fourth Princess Yaoyao =

21
00:01:36,620 --> 00:01:39,260
Madam, it’s my fault.

22
00:01:40,260 --> 00:01:41,420
Please calm down.

23
00:01:41,780 --> 00:01:42,980
Yaoyao went out, energetic,

24
00:01:42,980 --> 00:01:43,820
but came back motionless.

25
00:01:43,820 --> 00:01:44,820
You ask me to calm down?

26
00:01:45,860 --> 00:01:46,620
Madam.

27
00:01:47,420 --> 00:01:49,260
Punish me in whatever way you want.

28
00:01:49,780 --> 00:01:51,540
But don’t be too anxious.

29
00:01:52,300 --> 00:01:53,460
You’re pregnant.

30
00:01:53,700 --> 00:01:54,820
You mustn’t be anxious.

31
00:01:55,940 --> 00:01:57,060
It’s all my fault.

32
00:02:01,220 --> 00:02:01,860
How is it going?

33
00:02:01,940 --> 00:02:02,700
How is Yaoyao?

34
00:02:02,780 --> 00:02:03,900
Is she getting better?

35
00:02:04,340 --> 00:02:05,740
The princess is all right for now.

36
00:02:06,380 --> 00:02:07,860
The medicine she took

37
00:02:07,860 --> 00:02:09,020
helps to calm the nerves.

38
00:02:09,420 --> 00:02:10,620
She’s now asleep.

39
00:02:11,780 --> 00:02:12,860
What do you mean for now?

40
00:02:13,140 --> 00:02:16,780
She got her lung hurt and gasped...

41
00:02:17,060 --> 00:02:18,500
I want no more unintelligible words.

42
00:02:18,780 --> 00:02:19,980
I just need you to tell me

43
00:02:19,980 --> 00:02:21,380
how Yaoyao is keeping.

44
00:02:21,500 --> 00:02:22,300
Will she be all right

45
00:02:22,300 --> 00:02:23,020
after she wakes up?

46
00:02:24,500 --> 00:02:27,540
I’ll make a prescription for her.

47
00:02:28,060 --> 00:02:30,380
But she was nearly suffocated.

48
00:02:30,500 --> 00:02:32,660
She’s young and weak.

49
00:02:33,020 --> 00:02:34,740
As for complete cure...

50
00:02:34,900 --> 00:02:36,340
Sometimes you get her weaker

51
00:02:36,340 --> 00:02:37,300
and sometimes you can’t heal her.

52
00:02:37,380 --> 00:02:38,580
What do I need you for?

53
00:02:38,940 --> 00:02:39,980
Don’t get angry, madam.

54
00:02:39,980 --> 00:02:40,620
Madam Zhang.

55
00:02:40,620 --> 00:02:41,420
Madam.

56
00:02:42,100 --> 00:02:43,500
Don’t disturb the princess.

57
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:44,540
If she gasps again,

58
00:02:44,540 --> 00:02:45,620
she might be in danger.

59
00:02:46,980 --> 00:02:47,740
It’s you?

60
00:02:48,620 --> 00:02:49,660
Why are you here?

61
00:02:50,020 --> 00:02:53,500
Madam, she saved the princess.

62
00:02:53,980 --> 00:02:54,700
Madam.

63
00:02:55,260 --> 00:02:57,660
Luckily, Qiuhe did acupuncture to the princess,

64
00:02:57,820 --> 00:03:00,460
stopped her from gasping

65
00:03:00,540 --> 00:03:02,980
and gave her some medicinal powder

66
00:03:03,500 --> 00:03:06,420
to keep her from being suffocated.

67
00:03:06,740 --> 00:03:08,980
Otherwise, she might...

68
00:03:12,220 --> 00:03:13,540
Why were you there?

69
00:03:14,780 --> 00:03:16,220
I heard Aunt Jia yell for help

70
00:03:16,500 --> 00:03:17,700
so I went to have a look.

71
00:03:18,380 --> 00:03:20,620
The princess could hardly breathe.

72
00:03:21,180 --> 00:03:22,100
Under such emergency,

73
00:03:22,180 --> 00:03:23,820
I had to puncture her with my hairpin

74
00:03:24,220 --> 00:03:26,380
and feed her the medicinal powder for relief.

75
00:03:27,500 --> 00:03:29,580
I overstepped my authority

76
00:03:29,580 --> 00:03:30,620
and acted rudely.

77
00:03:31,300 --> 00:03:32,340
Please forgive me, madam.

78
00:03:36,900 --> 00:03:37,980
You saved my daughter.

79
00:03:39,260 --> 00:03:40,500
Whether it’s out of your kindness or not,

80
00:03:41,540 --> 00:03:42,820
you helped a lot.

81
00:03:43,980 --> 00:03:44,740
Aunt.

82
00:03:45,740 --> 00:03:47,420
Go get her five-dou South Sea Pearls,

83
00:03:47,980 --> 00:03:49,060
a pair of jade bracelets

84
00:03:50,380 --> 00:03:51,780
and two shoe-shaped gold.

85
00:03:52,740 --> 00:03:53,380
Aye.

86
00:03:54,140 --> 00:03:55,020
Go, madam.

87
00:03:55,580 --> 00:03:56,660
Thank you, madam.

88
00:03:56,660 --> 00:03:57,780
Go sit down.

89
00:04:11,860 --> 00:04:12,860
Seems like

90
00:04:13,100 --> 00:04:15,300
the princess had the asthma from pollen.

91
00:04:15,900 --> 00:04:17,020
If it attacks again,

92
00:04:17,260 --> 00:04:18,500
she’ll be in more danger.

93
00:04:19,820 --> 00:04:21,100
Maids who take care of princess

94
00:04:22,260 --> 00:04:23,660
must be more careful.

95
00:04:28,420 --> 00:04:29,700
I always know

96
00:04:31,620 --> 00:04:33,660
Huirou isn’t good at studying.

97
00:04:34,860 --> 00:04:36,100
She wants to go to the Imperial School

98
00:04:36,780 --> 00:04:37,620
only because

99
00:04:38,380 --> 00:04:39,540
she feels bored

100
00:04:39,540 --> 00:04:40,460
when she lives

101
00:04:40,540 --> 00:04:42,060
in such a small place

102
00:04:42,660 --> 00:04:43,380
with so few people around her.

103
00:04:45,580 --> 00:04:46,900
In the Imperial School,

104
00:04:47,180 --> 00:04:48,780
she can meet different people

105
00:04:48,900 --> 00:04:50,420
and listen to news.

106
00:04:51,820 --> 00:04:53,580
Just because of her curiosity,

107
00:04:55,140 --> 00:04:56,700
she talks wildly

108
00:04:56,700 --> 00:04:57,900
at such a young age.

109
00:05:01,060 --> 00:05:03,180
You’re going to open the Hall of Articles

110
00:05:03,740 --> 00:05:05,100
and write down the imperial edict

111
00:05:05,980 --> 00:05:07,340
to fire redundant officials

112
00:05:07,620 --> 00:05:09,940
and to reform the standards for imperial exams.

113
00:05:10,580 --> 00:05:12,180
People will be uneasy.

114
00:05:12,340 --> 00:05:14,220
Everyone wants to know your attitude.

115
00:05:15,780 --> 00:05:17,420
Huirou is a princess.

116
00:05:18,060 --> 00:05:19,500
Mr. Shi of the Imperial School

117
00:05:19,580 --> 00:05:20,780
likes to talk about politics.

118
00:05:21,420 --> 00:05:22,740
Her unintentional words

119
00:05:23,220 --> 00:05:24,740
will make people guess.

120
00:05:30,940 --> 00:05:31,980
Unexpectedly,

121
00:05:33,460 --> 00:05:35,540
Huirou is the first to be injured.

122
00:05:40,460 --> 00:05:41,260
Your Majesty.

123
00:05:43,260 --> 00:05:44,700
Huirou is your eldest daughter.

124
00:05:47,100 --> 00:05:48,940
She has her duty.

125
00:06:02,820 --> 00:06:04,060
Since I knew Madam Miao was pregnant,

126
00:06:05,460 --> 00:06:07,060
I had expected a baby girl.

127
00:06:08,540 --> 00:06:09,620
That was because

128
00:06:09,820 --> 00:06:11,620
I didn’t want my favorite child

129
00:06:12,260 --> 00:06:14,020
to be restrained

130
00:06:14,140 --> 00:06:16,580
by family or state responsibilities.

131
00:06:18,060 --> 00:06:19,420
She would never enjoy the real happiness

132
00:06:21,180 --> 00:06:23,060
in the palace.

133
00:06:47,500 --> 00:06:50,060
Since I married you,

134
00:06:51,100 --> 00:06:53,780
I’ve insisted on telling you what I should.

135
00:06:54,260 --> 00:06:55,940
If I say something wrong

136
00:06:56,380 --> 00:06:57,140
or something improper

137
00:06:57,500 --> 00:06:58,700
to have annoyed you

138
00:07:00,100 --> 00:07:01,460
and what I said becomes one of the reasons

139
00:07:01,460 --> 00:07:03,220
that make you unhappy,

140
00:07:05,860 --> 00:07:07,260
I’ve got nothing to argue.

141
00:07:09,460 --> 00:07:11,500
Please punish me.

142
00:07:29,020 --> 00:07:29,860
What are you doing?

143
00:07:30,300 --> 00:07:31,140
What do you think you are doing?

144
00:07:32,220 --> 00:07:33,700
I didn’t say you made a wrong decision!

145
00:07:33,980 --> 00:07:34,860
I just...

146
00:07:35,900 --> 00:07:37,220
I just feel sorry for Huirou.

147
00:07:37,940 --> 00:07:39,180
But you risk your life

148
00:07:39,180 --> 00:07:40,300
to advise me like a censor.

149
00:07:47,620 --> 00:07:48,780
I wonder where I am,

150
00:07:49,700 --> 00:07:51,860
the harem or the court?

151
00:07:52,300 --> 00:07:53,500
And who are you?

152
00:07:53,500 --> 00:07:54,580
My empress, Deputy Censor,

153
00:07:54,580 --> 00:07:55,700
Left Censor or Right Censor?

154
00:08:08,740 --> 00:08:10,420
Since the wedding day,

155
00:08:13,740 --> 00:08:16,020
I’ve only been the Empress of Song.

156
00:08:18,860 --> 00:08:20,540
You’ve never treated me

157
00:08:20,540 --> 00:08:21,940
as your wife.

158
00:08:25,420 --> 00:08:26,620
Since so,

159
00:08:27,660 --> 00:08:29,500
I always deal with problems,

160
00:08:29,980 --> 00:08:32,220
in the name of the Empress only

161
00:08:33,900 --> 00:08:35,300
and I don’t dare to be careless.

162
00:08:37,820 --> 00:08:38,940
The princess has serious illness.

163
00:08:39,020 --> 00:08:40,180
Madam Zhang, who is pregnant

164
00:08:40,180 --> 00:08:41,020
is bleeding with worry.

165
00:08:41,060 --> 00:08:42,540
But you stop me from seeing His Majesty.

166
00:08:42,540 --> 00:08:43,580
If Madam Zhang is in danger,

167
00:08:43,580 --> 00:08:44,580
can you take the blame?

168
00:08:46,380 --> 00:08:47,140
Your Majesty!

169
00:08:55,420 --> 00:08:56,500
See you, Your Majesty.

170
00:09:43,780 --> 00:09:48,980
= Imperial Pharmacy =

171
00:09:53,500 --> 00:09:54,540
The princess seems

172
00:09:54,780 --> 00:09:55,540
to have the asthma

173
00:09:55,540 --> 00:09:57,540
caused by pollen.

174
00:09:57,980 --> 00:09:59,380
I have the same problem.

175
00:10:00,300 --> 00:10:02,900
I always take the first-aid medicine with me.

176
00:10:03,500 --> 00:10:06,100
It works for the princess, too.

177
00:10:07,100 --> 00:10:08,420
But I don’t understand.

178
00:10:09,300 --> 00:10:11,020
The problem usually happens

179
00:10:11,020 --> 00:10:12,900
at the end of spring and the beginning of summer.

180
00:10:14,060 --> 00:10:15,980
Why did she

181
00:10:16,140 --> 00:10:18,580
suddenly have it in autumn?

182
00:10:19,820 --> 00:10:21,100
May I ask

183
00:10:21,860 --> 00:10:23,340
if the princess also has running nose,

184
00:10:23,580 --> 00:10:25,500
tearful eyes,

185
00:10:25,780 --> 00:10:26,860
or skin rashes

186
00:10:27,300 --> 00:10:29,140
in spring?

187
00:10:31,060 --> 00:10:32,020
To be honest,

188
00:10:32,780 --> 00:10:34,380
I have the same doubt.

189
00:10:34,460 --> 00:10:35,300
Therefore,

190
00:10:35,620 --> 00:10:37,420
I just checked the records of the princess.

191
00:10:37,420 --> 00:10:38,500
Yes, she has.

192
00:10:39,860 --> 00:10:42,020
During the blooming season of paper mulberries?

193
00:10:42,580 --> 00:10:43,340
Yes.

194
00:10:43,900 --> 00:10:46,100
She coughed and gasped for some days.

195
00:10:46,540 --> 00:10:47,780
Physician Wang checked up on her.

196
00:10:48,300 --> 00:10:50,340
But not as badly as this time.

197
00:10:50,980 --> 00:10:52,740
She suddenly had the asthma,

198
00:10:52,860 --> 00:10:53,700
maybe...

199
00:10:54,500 --> 00:10:55,900
There were other flower trees

200
00:10:56,060 --> 00:10:58,260
in the backyard

201
00:10:58,780 --> 00:11:00,100
or she has some other unknown disease.

202
00:11:01,100 --> 00:11:03,940
You saved the princess fearlessly.

203
00:11:04,820 --> 00:11:07,020
You want to know why she fell ill

204
00:11:07,660 --> 00:11:09,220
in case of another attack.

205
00:11:09,620 --> 00:11:10,940
It’s so kind of you.

206
00:11:11,740 --> 00:11:13,060
I really admire that.

207
00:11:14,980 --> 00:11:16,620
My colleagues and I

208
00:11:16,620 --> 00:11:18,220
will try our best to find out the reason

209
00:11:18,460 --> 00:11:19,500
and the precautions.

210
00:11:20,340 --> 00:11:21,700
But, miss,

211
00:11:22,260 --> 00:11:23,660
you’re still young.

212
00:11:24,580 --> 00:11:27,260
You’re in the palace for only two or three years.

213
00:11:28,100 --> 00:11:30,220
There’s something you don’t understand.

214
00:11:30,820 --> 00:11:32,300
You mustn’t talk widely

215
00:11:32,420 --> 00:11:33,740
about matters regarding the royal family.

216
00:11:34,300 --> 00:11:35,980
Otherwise, something you say unintentionally

217
00:11:36,500 --> 00:11:38,660
might cause great trouble.

218
00:11:42,180 --> 00:11:43,260
Thank you for your instruction.

219
00:12:00,300 --> 00:12:01,140
You walk so smoothly.

220
00:12:01,140 --> 00:12:02,820
Come. Why don’t you have a rest?

221
00:12:04,940 --> 00:12:06,140
Still want to walk?

222
00:12:49,740 --> 00:12:50,900
It’s okay. It’s okay.

223
00:12:52,420 --> 00:12:53,620
The physician said

224
00:12:53,860 --> 00:12:55,300
you were too frightened.

225
00:12:55,460 --> 00:12:56,580
The baby is all right.

226
00:12:56,900 --> 00:12:58,380
You just need to take more rest.

227
00:12:59,900 --> 00:13:01,260
Yaoyao will be fine, too.

228
00:13:03,140 --> 00:13:04,660
She coughs sometimes.

229
00:13:06,180 --> 00:13:08,620
But if she gets recuperation and doesn’t fall ill,

230
00:13:08,740 --> 00:13:09,820
she’ll totally recover

231
00:13:09,900 --> 00:13:11,380
in one year or two.

232
00:13:12,500 --> 00:13:16,780
Bird’s nest clears away the lung heat, doesn’t it?

233
00:13:17,540 --> 00:13:20,660
I’ll keep all the bird’s nests from Lopburi Kingdom

234
00:13:20,780 --> 00:13:22,060
for Yaoyao.

235
00:13:25,260 --> 00:13:26,540
I’m so scared.

236
00:13:28,140 --> 00:13:30,860
Yaoyao was such a good baby before she was born.

237
00:13:31,220 --> 00:13:32,500
She didn’t trouble me at all.

238
00:13:33,820 --> 00:13:35,020
Since she was born,

239
00:13:35,580 --> 00:13:37,060
I had taken care of her every day

240
00:13:37,700 --> 00:13:39,540
until her hundredth day.

241
00:13:40,740 --> 00:13:41,740
Finally,

242
00:13:42,500 --> 00:13:44,220
she is growing up.

243
00:13:45,340 --> 00:13:46,460
She calls me mother

244
00:13:46,780 --> 00:13:47,860
and calls you father.

245
00:13:48,620 --> 00:13:51,820
She sits, crawls and walks.

246
00:13:53,260 --> 00:13:55,340
When I find I’m pregnant again,

247
00:13:55,900 --> 00:13:57,340
I fail to keep an eye on her all the time.

248
00:13:58,900 --> 00:14:00,340
Then something went wrong.

249
00:14:04,020 --> 00:14:04,620
Don’t be scared.

250
00:14:06,820 --> 00:14:07,780
I’ll be with you.

251
00:14:08,780 --> 00:14:10,020
I’ll come and stay with you

252
00:14:10,500 --> 00:14:12,620
until you deliver the baby and Yaoyao gets better.

253
00:14:13,780 --> 00:14:15,500
I promise I’ll come every day.

254
00:14:18,220 --> 00:14:19,020
Your Majesty.

255
00:14:19,380 --> 00:14:22,420
Don’t... Don’t fool me.

256
00:14:24,100 --> 00:14:25,220
An emperor always keeps his words.

257
00:14:31,500 --> 00:14:32,220
Your Majesty.

258
00:14:33,900 --> 00:14:35,820
Please demote me.

259
00:14:37,460 --> 00:14:38,180
What?

260
00:14:39,300 --> 00:14:40,780
I guess I’m too unlucky.

261
00:14:41,140 --> 00:14:42,700
I don’t deserve so much love from you.

262
00:14:43,220 --> 00:14:45,140
That’s why others hate me.

263
00:14:45,820 --> 00:14:47,580
Chuyue died because of the curse.

264
00:14:47,700 --> 00:14:49,220
And Yaoyao is sick.

265
00:14:49,220 --> 00:14:50,380
I’m really scared.

266
00:14:51,140 --> 00:14:53,660
But if I let you care less for me,

267
00:14:53,660 --> 00:14:55,060
and visit other madams more often,

268
00:14:56,100 --> 00:14:57,460
I would rather

269
00:14:57,460 --> 00:14:58,340
kill myself!

270
00:15:00,020 --> 00:15:02,020
So, please demote me,

271
00:15:02,100 --> 00:15:03,100
to make others hate us less

272
00:15:03,700 --> 00:15:05,460
and store up blessings

273
00:15:05,460 --> 00:15:06,220
for Yaoyao and the baby.

274
00:15:07,420 --> 00:15:08,740
As long as you love us

275
00:15:09,860 --> 00:15:11,540
and our children can grow up healthily,

276
00:15:12,300 --> 00:15:13,220
I would be glad

277
00:15:13,220 --> 00:15:14,220
even if I have to be an inferior Lady

278
00:15:14,460 --> 00:15:15,500
all my life.

279
00:15:18,740 --> 00:15:20,100
I swear.

280
00:15:20,260 --> 00:15:21,580
I’m telling the truth.

281
00:15:21,740 --> 00:15:23,500
Let me die if I tell any lie.

282
00:15:46,220 --> 00:15:47,300
I expect nothing else.

283
00:15:48,020 --> 00:15:49,540
As long as my husband loves me,

284
00:15:50,140 --> 00:15:51,140
and my children are healthy,

285
00:15:52,380 --> 00:15:53,100
I will be grateful

286
00:15:53,580 --> 00:15:55,300
to the heaven

287
00:15:55,860 --> 00:15:57,220
even if I’ll never be promoted again.

288
00:16:15,380 --> 00:16:16,060
Aunt.

289
00:16:19,580 --> 00:16:20,340
You did that.

290
00:16:20,660 --> 00:16:23,100
= Xu Lantiao =

291
00:16:23,100 --> 00:16:24,260
What do you mean?

292
00:16:27,740 --> 00:16:28,980
Stop pretending!

293
00:16:31,580 --> 00:16:32,900
You get back all the clothes and handkerchiefs

294
00:16:33,660 --> 00:16:35,700
for ironing and fumigating.

295
00:16:37,420 --> 00:16:38,980
Why does this handkerchief

296
00:16:39,620 --> 00:16:40,660
have so much pollen of

297
00:16:40,660 --> 00:16:42,420
paper mulberry flowers?

298
00:16:43,580 --> 00:16:44,340
Besides,

299
00:16:44,980 --> 00:16:46,140
why are there so many paper mulberries

300
00:16:46,860 --> 00:16:48,460
out of Bihan’s windows?

301
00:16:51,380 --> 00:16:52,340
Then why didn’t you tie me

302
00:16:53,580 --> 00:16:55,380
and take me to Madam Zhang?

303
00:16:57,540 --> 00:16:58,580
With testimony, evidence,

304
00:17:00,220 --> 00:17:01,380
and confirmation from physicians,

305
00:17:01,380 --> 00:17:02,740
even if I’ll be killed right away,

306
00:17:03,540 --> 00:17:05,340
His Majesty will not show any mercy.

307
00:17:06,860 --> 00:17:07,900
Then why haven’t you done that?

308
00:17:10,100 --> 00:17:10,900
I extracted and boiled

309
00:17:11,220 --> 00:17:12,980
the pollen of paper mulberry flowers

310
00:17:14,380 --> 00:17:16,940
and put it on this handkerchief.

311
00:17:18,860 --> 00:17:20,580
But it was you who used it

312
00:17:21,540 --> 00:17:22,620
to wipe the princess’s mouth.

313
00:17:24,780 --> 00:17:26,540
Lately, because of Chief Xia,

314
00:17:27,420 --> 00:17:28,380
you need to use Huaimin and me

315
00:17:29,580 --> 00:17:31,460
to get the information

316
00:17:31,900 --> 00:17:32,820
and contact old friends.

317
00:17:33,820 --> 00:17:35,220
You’ve been close to me.

318
00:17:36,900 --> 00:17:38,100
Suspicious as Madam Zhang is,

319
00:17:39,220 --> 00:17:40,220
do you think she will

320
00:17:41,020 --> 00:17:42,540
suspect you and vent her anger on you?

321
00:17:46,700 --> 00:17:48,020
Are you threatening me?

322
00:17:51,580 --> 00:17:53,060
How dare you!

323
00:17:53,260 --> 00:17:54,300
You threaten me?

324
00:17:54,300 --> 00:17:55,500
How audacious you are!

325
00:17:56,260 --> 00:17:57,260
You threaten me?

326
00:17:57,500 --> 00:17:58,300
Let go of her!

327
00:17:58,300 --> 00:17:59,060
What are you doing?

328
00:18:02,220 --> 00:18:03,460
How dare you threaten me again!

329
00:18:04,220 --> 00:18:05,660
= Yang Huaimin =
I warned you

330
00:18:05,660 --> 00:18:07,140
not to act recklessly.

331
00:18:07,420 --> 00:18:09,700
Dong Qiuhe is a smart girl.

332
00:18:10,180 --> 00:18:12,060
If she sees us through,

333
00:18:12,300 --> 00:18:13,660
and tells Madam Zhang,

334
00:18:13,660 --> 00:18:15,060
she’ll burn this place

335
00:18:15,060 --> 00:18:16,420
and we’ll be screwed.

336
00:18:24,740 --> 00:18:26,300
Qiuhe came to me with the handkerchief.

337
00:18:26,500 --> 00:18:27,820
I had to admit it.

338
00:18:28,340 --> 00:18:29,220
I told her

339
00:18:29,300 --> 00:18:30,580
we didn’t usually use

340
00:18:30,580 --> 00:18:31,620
ordinary incenses.

341
00:18:32,180 --> 00:18:33,220
In the incenses,

342
00:18:33,300 --> 00:18:34,620
some pollen of paper mulberry flowers is mixed.

343
00:18:35,620 --> 00:18:36,660
She only told me

344
00:18:36,700 --> 00:18:37,900
not to use any pollen again.

345
00:18:38,580 --> 00:18:39,860
I’m warning you now.

346
00:18:40,380 --> 00:18:41,980
Even if it’s Xia Song’s order,

347
00:18:43,500 --> 00:18:44,420
when anyone dares

348
00:18:44,700 --> 00:18:46,740
to hurt Yaoyao again,

349
00:18:47,740 --> 00:18:49,540
I’ll risk my life to protect her!

350
00:18:49,540 --> 00:18:50,460
What makes you so irritable?

351
00:18:52,900 --> 00:18:53,660
It has nothing to do

352
00:18:53,700 --> 00:18:55,300
with Chief Xia or me.

353
00:18:55,980 --> 00:18:57,500
She did the crazy thing.

354
00:18:59,220 --> 00:19:01,140
From so much trouble,

355
00:19:01,140 --> 00:19:02,300
we’ll get nothing beneficial.

356
00:19:02,300 --> 00:19:03,900
How could Chief Xia give such an order?

357
00:19:04,180 --> 00:19:06,060
It’s just the resentment among women.

358
00:19:12,580 --> 00:19:13,620
Anyway,

359
00:19:14,420 --> 00:19:15,940
it’s good to annoy Madam Zhang.

360
00:19:16,780 --> 00:19:18,740
Anyway, she’ll hate the Empress

361
00:19:18,740 --> 00:19:19,780
and Madam Miao.

362
00:19:20,300 --> 00:19:22,260
All these years,

363
00:19:22,260 --> 00:19:23,220
Chief Xia promoted her uncle

364
00:19:23,220 --> 00:19:24,660
and spent so much money

365
00:19:24,660 --> 00:19:26,380
drawing people in,

366
00:19:26,740 --> 00:19:28,540
not because he wants her to be

367
00:19:28,540 --> 00:19:30,220
a mere lady of His Majesty with a daughter.

368
00:19:30,220 --> 00:19:31,500
You can’t force Bihan.

369
00:19:32,260 --> 00:19:33,820
Stop doing anything stupid.

370
00:19:34,580 --> 00:19:36,100
I will persuade her.

371
00:19:38,180 --> 00:19:39,060
As for her,

372
00:19:40,980 --> 00:19:42,500
I won’t let her go.

373
00:19:42,740 --> 00:19:44,100
You hit her and pinched her.

374
00:19:44,100 --> 00:19:45,020
What else do you want?

375
00:19:45,380 --> 00:19:46,220
If you keep beating her

376
00:19:46,420 --> 00:19:48,260
and let Zhang Maoze find it fishy,

377
00:19:48,260 --> 00:19:49,380
are you going to get screwed?

378
00:19:56,700 --> 00:19:58,260
Don’t stare at her

379
00:19:58,260 --> 00:19:59,100
like a decent woman.

380
00:19:59,740 --> 00:20:01,580
You smuggled things

381
00:20:01,580 --> 00:20:02,940
and sold girls.

382
00:20:04,500 --> 00:20:06,980
You even sell untaxed salt.

383
00:20:08,180 --> 00:20:09,980
Do you want Zhang Maoze to find out

384
00:20:09,980 --> 00:20:11,780
that Chief Xia embezzled money?

385
00:20:16,860 --> 00:20:17,860
All right.

386
00:20:20,260 --> 00:20:21,060
Fine.

387
00:20:44,380 --> 00:20:45,900
Can’t recite the poem again?

388
00:20:46,420 --> 00:20:47,940
What do you mean again?

389
00:20:48,100 --> 00:20:48,980
Why do you say that too?

390
00:20:49,700 --> 00:20:50,780
Even you mock me.

391
00:20:54,980 --> 00:20:56,100
I’m sorry, princess.

392
00:20:56,580 --> 00:20:57,500
Please punish me.

393
00:20:58,700 --> 00:21:00,420
Do you think I don’t dare to?

394
00:21:13,980 --> 00:21:16,260
Why does no one love me?

395
00:21:24,060 --> 00:21:25,500
Everyone loves you, princess.

396
00:21:26,460 --> 00:21:27,540
No.

397
00:21:27,660 --> 00:21:29,020
No one.

398
00:21:29,020 --> 00:21:30,060
None of you loves me.

399
00:21:31,100 --> 00:21:33,380
I’m grumpy and stupid.

400
00:21:33,580 --> 00:21:34,980
I can’t recite poems.

401
00:21:36,780 --> 00:21:38,620
You’re the most beautiful and lovely girl.

402
00:21:39,780 --> 00:21:40,780
In my heart,

403
00:21:41,300 --> 00:21:42,460
you’re like a fairy.

404
00:21:53,820 --> 00:21:55,500
All right, princess.

405
00:21:58,380 --> 00:21:59,460
Stop crying.

406
00:22:00,380 --> 00:22:01,500
His Majesty and Her Highness

407
00:22:01,700 --> 00:22:03,100
care for you the most.

408
00:22:03,660 --> 00:22:05,220
Madam Miao always defends you.

409
00:22:05,900 --> 00:22:06,620
I...

410
00:22:08,620 --> 00:22:10,260
I like you the most.

411
00:22:10,820 --> 00:22:12,580
Hope I’ll always serve you.

412
00:22:16,220 --> 00:22:17,620
You are lying to make me happy.

413
00:22:19,780 --> 00:22:20,780
I never lie.

414
00:22:22,140 --> 00:22:24,020
How many times have I told you

415
00:22:24,340 --> 00:22:26,260
not to kneel when no one else is around?

416
00:22:27,420 --> 00:22:29,340
When I share snacks with you,

417
00:22:29,380 --> 00:22:30,500
don’t say thank you.

418
00:22:30,580 --> 00:22:32,540
Take whatever I give you.

419
00:22:32,780 --> 00:22:36,180
I... I only lose temper on you.

420
00:22:36,860 --> 00:22:39,140
I don’t always lose temper on anyone else.

421
00:22:39,140 --> 00:22:40,140
Never.

422
00:22:41,300 --> 00:22:42,700
Don’t always stay far from me

423
00:22:42,700 --> 00:22:44,740
when you ask for punishment.

424
00:22:50,300 --> 00:22:51,220
Huaiji.

425
00:22:51,740 --> 00:22:53,660
Do you remember what I said?

426
00:22:58,140 --> 00:22:59,020
Brother.

427
00:22:59,620 --> 00:23:01,660
Do you remember what I said?

428
00:23:07,540 --> 00:23:10,420
Yes. I’ll never forget.

429
00:23:13,140 --> 00:23:14,580
You’re still lying.

430
00:23:18,980 --> 00:23:20,420
You said you would always accompany me.

431
00:23:20,820 --> 00:23:22,620
But now you only come to paint with me

432
00:23:22,620 --> 00:23:24,020
every three or four days.

433
00:23:25,380 --> 00:23:26,900
You’re father’s.

434
00:23:31,620 --> 00:23:32,460
When I came,

435
00:23:32,460 --> 00:23:33,940
I saw you crying.

436
00:23:34,820 --> 00:23:35,860
I didn’t have time

437
00:23:35,860 --> 00:23:36,820
to tell you the order from His Majesty.

438
00:23:39,700 --> 00:23:40,660
His Majesty asked me

439
00:23:40,900 --> 00:23:42,700
to come to study with you

440
00:23:42,900 --> 00:23:43,980
after three o’clock every afternoon.

441
00:23:44,660 --> 00:23:45,580
If you don’t understand anything

442
00:23:45,980 --> 00:23:47,740
the Imperial Recorder teaches you,

443
00:23:48,420 --> 00:23:50,820
I need to try my best to explain to you.

444
00:23:51,540 --> 00:23:52,620
If you’re interested in something

445
00:23:52,620 --> 00:23:54,620
but the Imperial Recorder doesn’t teach you,

446
00:23:54,660 --> 00:23:55,820
you can tell me.

447
00:23:56,620 --> 00:23:57,620
His Majesty said

448
00:23:57,820 --> 00:23:59,780
I could go to all important officials

449
00:24:00,340 --> 00:24:01,780
with your question

450
00:24:01,780 --> 00:24:02,900
and ask them

451
00:24:03,180 --> 00:24:04,140
about it.

452
00:24:05,180 --> 00:24:06,740
Then I can tell you

453
00:24:06,820 --> 00:24:07,660
their instructions.

454
00:24:11,220 --> 00:24:13,100
I know father loves me the most.

455
00:24:13,380 --> 00:24:14,380
Father is the best.

456
00:24:14,780 --> 00:24:16,020
He cares for me the most.

457
00:24:16,340 --> 00:24:18,140
When you can come to me every day,

458
00:24:18,140 --> 00:24:19,940
it’s better than studying in the Imperial School.

459
00:24:22,620 --> 00:24:24,220
Let’s go find something to eat.

460
00:24:24,780 --> 00:24:27,180
I was angry with mother and Her Highness

461
00:24:27,820 --> 00:24:28,580
and I said I wasn’t hungry.

462
00:24:28,940 --> 00:24:29,780
Mother said

463
00:24:31,380 --> 00:24:32,740
“Don’t eat then.

464
00:24:32,900 --> 00:24:34,460
You’re getting fat, anyway.”

465
00:24:34,820 --> 00:24:36,500
Huaiji, do I get fat?

466
00:24:41,980 --> 00:24:42,900
Not at all.

467
00:24:43,820 --> 00:24:46,060
You’re sad these days,

468
00:24:46,260 --> 00:24:47,220
so you look somehow slimmer.

469
00:24:47,820 --> 00:24:48,660
That’s fine, then.

470
00:24:49,260 --> 00:24:50,420
I know there are mutton buns

471
00:24:50,420 --> 00:24:51,940
and stewed fish soup in the kitchen.

472
00:24:52,260 --> 00:24:54,060
Go heat them for me.

473
00:24:54,420 --> 00:24:55,700
I’m starving.

474
00:24:57,100 --> 00:24:57,780
Aye.

475
00:24:58,460 --> 00:24:59,100
Let’s go.

476
00:25:03,100 --> 00:25:03,860
Prime Minister Yan.

477
00:25:06,780 --> 00:25:08,740
= Su Shunqin, courtesy name Zimei =
Based on His Majesty’s instruction,

478
00:25:08,860 --> 00:25:09,500
the Imperial Academy made new standards

479
00:25:09,500 --> 00:25:11,020
for the spring exam next year.

480
00:25:11,340 --> 00:25:12,940
Focus on the principles of articles.

481
00:25:13,020 --> 00:25:14,340
Focus on the discourse on politics.

482
00:25:14,700 --> 00:25:15,340
= Yan Shu, courtesy name Tongshu =
Articles on country ruling

483
00:25:15,380 --> 00:25:16,900
are limited.

484
00:25:17,860 --> 00:25:18,900
Please have a look.

485
00:25:27,660 --> 00:25:28,500
Prime Minister Zhang.

486
00:25:28,860 --> 00:25:31,780
= Zhang Dexiang, courtesy name Xiyan =

487
00:25:31,780 --> 00:25:33,260
It’s been only two months
since Fan Zhongyan carried out the reform

488
00:25:33,620 --> 00:25:36,620
under the instruction of His Majesty.

489
00:25:37,380 --> 00:25:39,020
Hundreds of officials have been dismissed

490
00:25:39,140 --> 00:25:41,500
in and around the Capital.

491
00:25:42,420 --> 00:25:45,460
Most of them have made no big mistakes.

492
00:25:50,340 --> 00:25:52,420
I remember these guys.

493
00:25:53,020 --> 00:25:54,540
Some of those officials in the Capital

494
00:25:54,820 --> 00:25:56,700
were involved in Feng Shiyuan’s case.

495
00:25:57,300 --> 00:25:59,700
Because they took no bribes,

496
00:25:59,980 --> 00:26:02,180
they weren’t imprisoned or banished.

497
00:26:02,420 --> 00:26:05,020
But they misjudged cases

498
00:26:05,500 --> 00:26:07,580
or didn’t carry out important law in their places

499
00:26:07,580 --> 00:26:09,620
for three or five years.

500
00:26:10,060 --> 00:26:11,780
Some are laggards

501
00:26:11,780 --> 00:26:13,700
who didn’t deal with cases

502
00:26:14,300 --> 00:26:16,100
in even one or two years.

503
00:26:16,740 --> 00:26:18,700
When His Majesty checked personally

504
00:26:18,780 --> 00:26:20,900
and found many incompetent officials,

505
00:26:21,580 --> 00:26:23,300
he didn’t punish them.

506
00:26:23,700 --> 00:26:25,620
But seen from current performance,

507
00:26:25,780 --> 00:26:28,180
they haven’t changed at all.

508
00:26:29,860 --> 00:26:30,940
I know.

509
00:26:31,500 --> 00:26:33,380
Fan Zhongyan must have a reason

510
00:26:33,380 --> 00:26:35,300
to dismiss incompetent officials.

511
00:26:35,900 --> 00:26:36,940
But...

512
00:26:37,420 --> 00:26:40,100
he has dismissed so many officials.

513
00:26:40,500 --> 00:26:42,460
People mostly became officials

514
00:26:42,460 --> 00:26:43,620
because of hard study for years

515
00:26:44,100 --> 00:26:46,620
or

516
00:26:46,620 --> 00:26:47,700
their ancestors’ contributions.

517
00:26:48,180 --> 00:26:49,700
When they’re dismissed,

518
00:26:50,060 --> 00:26:51,220
they’ll have no income.

519
00:26:51,820 --> 00:26:52,380
Well...

520
00:26:52,380 --> 00:26:53,140
Prime Minister Zhang.

521
00:26:56,580 --> 00:26:58,180
It’s the other way round, I think.

522
00:26:58,980 --> 00:26:59,780
We’re not

523
00:26:59,780 --> 00:27:01,220
taking away their posts or salaries.

524
00:27:01,780 --> 00:27:03,300
But they wrongly took

525
00:27:03,460 --> 00:27:04,940
the imperial salary

526
00:27:04,940 --> 00:27:05,940
and wasted people’s hard earnings.

527
00:27:06,380 --> 00:27:07,020
Besides,

528
00:27:07,660 --> 00:27:09,860
scholars study hard to become officials

529
00:27:10,060 --> 00:27:12,300
because they want to serve the country

530
00:27:12,340 --> 00:27:13,820
and help our people.

531
00:27:14,420 --> 00:27:16,140
Do they study hard

532
00:27:16,180 --> 00:27:17,780
only to come into the court

533
00:27:17,900 --> 00:27:19,180
and be a laggard

534
00:27:19,180 --> 00:27:20,420
all their lives?

535
00:27:20,620 --> 00:27:21,180
But...

536
00:27:21,220 --> 00:27:23,380
Besides, if a man’s ancestor made contributions,

537
00:27:23,500 --> 00:27:25,740
he should work harder, not to humiliate them.

538
00:27:25,980 --> 00:27:28,820
If he enjoys privileges without doing anything,

539
00:27:29,980 --> 00:27:31,580
he’ll be humiliating his family.

540
00:27:35,780 --> 00:27:37,340
Scholar Su,

541
00:27:37,620 --> 00:27:40,980
you were famous for articles at a young age.

542
00:27:41,500 --> 00:27:42,580
You’re from a noble family,

543
00:27:42,860 --> 00:27:44,940
but you don’t want an inherited post.

544
00:27:45,580 --> 00:27:47,140
You passed the imperial exam

545
00:27:47,620 --> 00:27:49,860
= Jia Changchao, courtesy name Ziming =
and were selected to work here.

546
00:27:51,060 --> 00:27:51,940
In your eyes,

547
00:27:52,380 --> 00:27:54,500
you don’t see any common people.

548
00:27:56,700 --> 00:27:59,300
If you want to criticize me for being arrogant,

549
00:27:59,460 --> 00:28:00,500
why don’t you say it directly?

550
00:28:00,740 --> 00:28:02,020
Don’t bother with the sarcasm.

551
00:28:02,180 --> 00:28:03,060
I don’t dare.

552
00:28:04,980 --> 00:28:08,260
You’re a talented man.

553
00:28:08,580 --> 00:28:10,940
You only see other talented men.

554
00:28:11,220 --> 00:28:12,860
Because you like the men of your level.

555
00:28:15,420 --> 00:28:18,340
Those who make friends with you

556
00:28:18,700 --> 00:28:21,100
must be famous talents

557
00:28:21,620 --> 00:28:24,380
instead of commoners.

558
00:28:25,020 --> 00:28:27,580
Even a commoner

559
00:28:27,700 --> 00:28:29,700
who passed the imperial exam,

560
00:28:29,740 --> 00:28:31,220
or the principle graduate His Majesty appointed

561
00:28:31,420 --> 00:28:32,820
fails to make friends with you, huh?

562
00:28:33,940 --> 00:28:34,740
We...

563
00:28:36,980 --> 00:28:40,060
= Wang Gongchen, courtesy name Junkuang =

564
00:28:43,780 --> 00:28:44,740
Sorry,

565
00:28:45,660 --> 00:28:46,740
I don’t understand

566
00:28:46,740 --> 00:28:47,620
the humor of talented scholars.

567
00:28:48,700 --> 00:28:49,700
I just feel

568
00:28:49,700 --> 00:28:50,780
it’s okay to

569
00:28:51,020 --> 00:28:52,380
tell such boring jokes

570
00:28:52,380 --> 00:28:53,220
from time to time.

571
00:28:53,580 --> 00:28:54,380
But why do you even make fun of it

572
00:28:54,380 --> 00:28:55,900
in the conference hall?

573
00:28:58,740 --> 00:28:59,540
Mr. Wang.

574
00:28:59,620 --> 00:29:00,340
Don’t talk to me.

575
00:29:07,180 --> 00:29:07,940
When you

576
00:29:07,940 --> 00:29:09,340
always talk about that,

577
00:29:09,340 --> 00:29:10,300
you will think

578
00:29:10,300 --> 00:29:11,460
all the others do the same thing.

579
00:29:12,340 --> 00:29:14,420
In fact, people easily forget it.

580
00:29:15,420 --> 00:29:16,100
Deputy Censor Wang.

581
00:29:16,140 --> 00:29:16,740
You...

582
00:29:23,940 --> 00:29:25,820
Do you have anything to report?

583
00:29:40,700 --> 00:29:41,620
Ten days ago,

584
00:29:42,620 --> 00:29:43,340
around Kaifeng,

585
00:29:43,380 --> 00:29:45,340
a 50-year-old county magistrate killed himself

586
00:29:45,540 --> 00:29:46,420
after he was dismissed,

587
00:29:47,100 --> 00:29:48,220
leaving his 80-year-old mother

588
00:29:48,500 --> 00:29:50,260
and five under-age children.

589
00:29:50,660 --> 00:29:52,620
They could reply on nothing to live now.

590
00:29:54,020 --> 00:29:55,500
More than a hundred dismissed officials from

591
00:29:55,700 --> 00:29:56,980
Jingdong West Province, Jingdong East Province,

592
00:29:57,220 --> 00:29:58,820
Hebei West Province and Hebei East Province

593
00:29:58,820 --> 00:29:59,820
have submitted a joint letter,

594
00:30:00,220 --> 00:30:02,660
asking His Majesty to care for his people

595
00:30:03,020 --> 00:30:03,980
and stop the harsh governing.

596
00:30:05,380 --> 00:30:06,900
Madam, do you know?

597
00:30:07,380 --> 00:30:10,500
That my husband married his late wife’s sister

598
00:30:10,620 --> 00:30:12,100
= Wang Gongchen’s Wife Xue Yuhu =
after his wife was just dead

599
00:30:12,500 --> 00:30:14,380
has been made up into a story

600
00:30:14,780 --> 00:30:17,900
and been told in all theatres.

601
00:30:19,300 --> 00:30:20,540
The other day,

602
00:30:21,300 --> 00:30:22,140
my husband

603
00:30:22,300 --> 00:30:24,500
even found two gossiping servants,

604
00:30:25,140 --> 00:30:25,980
who said that

605
00:30:26,820 --> 00:30:28,780
he fell in love

606
00:30:28,860 --> 00:30:30,540
with his sister-in-law

607
00:30:30,780 --> 00:30:32,380
when his ex-wife was carrying a baby

608
00:30:33,460 --> 00:30:35,140
and married me hurriedly

609
00:30:36,260 --> 00:30:38,660
after he forced his ex-wife to die.

610
00:30:41,260 --> 00:30:42,700
My husband was so angry that

611
00:30:43,100 --> 00:30:45,940
he wanted to send the servants to the government

612
00:30:46,700 --> 00:30:48,660
for the guilty of slandering their master.

613
00:30:50,060 --> 00:30:51,220
Unexpectedly, he got to know

614
00:30:53,020 --> 00:30:56,820
it was the latest story in theatres.

615
00:30:59,980 --> 00:31:00,940
Madam.

616
00:31:04,140 --> 00:31:06,380
I’ve done nothing wrong.

617
00:31:07,620 --> 00:31:09,020
Why must I be humiliated

618
00:31:09,660 --> 00:31:11,500
like that?

619
00:31:17,860 --> 00:31:19,580
I often think

620
00:31:20,540 --> 00:31:23,540
ladies are laughing at me.

621
00:31:26,180 --> 00:31:28,660
How can I still get on with them?

622
00:31:32,940 --> 00:31:34,100
If I didn’t need to

623
00:31:34,100 --> 00:31:35,700
take care of two children,

624
00:31:37,380 --> 00:31:39,980
I would even want to kill myself

625
00:31:41,060 --> 00:31:42,460
for vindication.

626
00:31:44,260 --> 00:31:45,820
You can’t be so weak.

627
00:31:46,900 --> 00:31:48,940
What do tears help?

628
00:31:49,460 --> 00:31:50,940
What does it help even if you kill yourself?

629
00:31:53,820 --> 00:31:55,220
You should answer blows with blows

630
00:31:56,380 --> 00:31:57,820
and take revenge.

631
00:31:59,100 --> 00:32:00,060
If I were you,

632
00:32:00,860 --> 00:32:02,500
when someone dared to humiliate my husband,

633
00:32:03,540 --> 00:32:06,980
I would ask him to pay the price ten times.

634
00:32:08,740 --> 00:32:10,820
Ten times?

635
00:32:11,860 --> 00:32:12,620
But...

636
00:32:13,100 --> 00:32:14,940
Excuse me,

637
00:32:16,580 --> 00:32:17,820
Deputy Censor Wang and Mrs. Wang

638
00:32:18,140 --> 00:32:19,660
were originally innocent.

639
00:32:19,980 --> 00:32:21,500
But the poems Ouyang Xiu wrote

640
00:32:21,500 --> 00:32:22,860
confused right and wrong.

641
00:32:23,780 --> 00:32:25,220
Is Ouyang Xiu really

642
00:32:26,140 --> 00:32:27,580
so innocent

643
00:32:27,940 --> 00:32:29,580
without any fault?

644
00:32:30,740 --> 00:32:33,100
He likes making poems, doesn’t he?

645
00:32:33,620 --> 00:32:34,940
He’s written so many poems.

646
00:32:35,460 --> 00:32:38,340
Isn’t there anything lecherous

647
00:32:38,700 --> 00:32:39,820
or rebellious?

648
00:32:41,540 --> 00:32:42,620
Ladies like us

649
00:32:42,660 --> 00:32:44,420
can’t understand those poems.

650
00:32:44,980 --> 00:32:45,980
But can’t the principle graduate

651
00:32:46,180 --> 00:32:48,060
find some faults from them?

652
00:32:53,620 --> 00:32:54,980
There are five additional regulations

653
00:32:55,260 --> 00:32:56,900
on cases where shops encroach the street

654
00:32:57,060 --> 00:32:58,820
and disturb the neighborhood.

655
00:32:59,460 --> 00:33:00,540
Please have a look, Your Majesty.

656
00:33:08,460 --> 00:33:09,540
Today is the Double Ninth Festival.

657
00:33:10,060 --> 00:33:11,460
There’s a party in the backyard.

658
00:33:12,780 --> 00:33:13,980
Why don’t you go back home early?

659
00:33:14,500 --> 00:33:16,460
Your parents died, just like mine.

660
00:33:16,580 --> 00:33:17,540
But you have an elder brother.

661
00:33:18,780 --> 00:33:22,340
Huaiji, go to the backyard with me

662
00:33:23,180 --> 00:33:24,300
and tell me

663
00:33:24,380 --> 00:33:25,780
how Huirou is doing with her study.

664
00:33:28,620 --> 00:33:30,620
Today, I’m going to meet my brother.

665
00:33:30,980 --> 00:33:32,620
My wife has gone to the party

666
00:33:32,660 --> 00:33:33,620
with the invitation.

667
00:33:34,260 --> 00:33:35,700
My brother wants to discuss

668
00:33:35,700 --> 00:33:36,900
about my eldest daughter’s marriage.

669
00:33:38,860 --> 00:33:40,220
Your eldest daughter is getting married?

670
00:33:42,500 --> 00:33:43,740
When I first met you,

671
00:33:44,340 --> 00:33:45,340
you weren’t married yet.

672
00:33:47,260 --> 00:33:48,220
Soon we met,

673
00:33:48,220 --> 00:33:49,940
you made me the second-place scholar.

674
00:33:50,260 --> 00:33:51,700
After that,

675
00:33:52,180 --> 00:33:53,740
I got married.

676
00:33:57,060 --> 00:33:58,580
Who is your daughter going to marry?

677
00:33:59,780 --> 00:34:00,980
Did you also

678
00:34:00,980 --> 00:34:02,580
keep an eye on the imperial exam?

679
00:34:03,300 --> 00:34:05,260
When you pick a talented young man,

680
00:34:05,500 --> 00:34:06,740
you take him back home?

681
00:34:07,700 --> 00:34:08,780
Don’t make fun of me, Your Majesty.

682
00:34:09,380 --> 00:34:10,260
When my daughter was little,

683
00:34:10,460 --> 00:34:12,020
she was engaged to Wen Yanbo’s eldest son.

684
00:34:12,860 --> 00:34:14,260
Wen Yanbo’s eldest son?

685
00:34:17,540 --> 00:34:18,380
Oh, I see.

686
00:34:18,820 --> 00:34:20,980
You and Wen Yanbo took the same imperial exam.

687
00:34:21,300 --> 00:34:23,420
I guess after you passed the exam,

688
00:34:23,420 --> 00:34:24,820
you got married successively

689
00:34:24,980 --> 00:34:26,580
and then had your children engaged.

690
00:34:27,380 --> 00:34:28,500
It’s wise of you, Your Majesty.

691
00:34:28,940 --> 00:34:30,700
Yes. Yes.

692
00:34:33,020 --> 00:34:35,980
His son passed the provincial exam last year.

693
00:34:36,140 --> 00:34:38,100
Next year, he’ll take the spring exam.

694
00:34:38,660 --> 00:34:41,100
You must have discussed about the marriage

695
00:34:41,140 --> 00:34:42,220
after he passed the exam.

696
00:34:43,740 --> 00:34:44,620
It’s our luck.

697
00:34:45,380 --> 00:34:46,620
Wen Yanbo’s son is well cultivated.

698
00:34:47,460 --> 00:34:48,740
They were engaged at a young age,

699
00:34:48,860 --> 00:34:50,340
even if he isn’t well cultivated,

700
00:34:50,380 --> 00:34:51,540
we would still let them marry.

701
00:34:56,140 --> 00:34:57,700
When you pick a husband for your daughter,

702
00:34:58,340 --> 00:34:59,660
you can pick from

703
00:34:59,660 --> 00:35:01,340
talented young men.

704
00:35:02,780 --> 00:35:04,020
But my daughter Huirou...

705
00:35:04,460 --> 00:35:05,820
I have to pick anyone but

706
00:35:05,820 --> 00:35:07,340
such talented men.

707
00:35:10,740 --> 00:35:12,460
Relatives used to interfere with politics,

708
00:35:12,660 --> 00:35:13,740
leading to the doom of the previous dynasties.

709
00:35:14,140 --> 00:35:15,380
Taking it as a warning,

710
00:35:15,700 --> 00:35:17,300
we never give power to relatives.

711
00:35:18,180 --> 00:35:19,380
If you want to marry a princess

712
00:35:19,380 --> 00:35:20,460
to a man in office

713
00:35:20,460 --> 00:35:21,740
who has real power,

714
00:35:22,340 --> 00:35:24,740
he will have a nominal title instead.

715
00:35:24,980 --> 00:35:26,220
He only has a good pay.

716
00:35:27,620 --> 00:35:29,100
Scholars are candidates for ministers.

717
00:35:29,460 --> 00:35:30,460
If one of them marry a princess,

718
00:35:30,860 --> 00:35:32,860
they can no longer realize their ambitions.

719
00:35:37,260 --> 00:35:38,620
It’s said that a princess easily finds a husband.

720
00:35:39,780 --> 00:35:41,900
And my daughter is so beautiful.

721
00:35:42,980 --> 00:35:43,740
But...

722
00:35:44,460 --> 00:35:46,260
if I pick a low-rank official for her,

723
00:35:46,980 --> 00:35:49,260
he would rather die than get married.

724
00:35:49,940 --> 00:35:52,460
Censors will say that I will ruin his career

725
00:35:52,820 --> 00:35:53,980
and try hard to stop me.

726
00:36:00,380 --> 00:36:01,980
Cui Bai’s four paintings

727
00:36:02,020 --> 00:36:03,780
enjoy popularity in the capital.

728
00:36:04,260 --> 00:36:06,980
The draft is widely used

729
00:36:07,620 --> 00:36:09,660
and embroidered on the fans, pouches,

730
00:36:09,660 --> 00:36:10,820
perfume boxes and screens.

731
00:36:11,500 --> 00:36:13,380
Girls in the capital also imitate

732
00:36:13,380 --> 00:36:15,300
your makeup and dress in the paintings,

733
00:36:15,620 --> 00:36:17,420
even the stewardesses’ soft hairband

734
00:36:17,420 --> 00:36:18,860
and dark shirt.

735
00:36:20,700 --> 00:36:22,700
Tipsy Breeze solid perfume balls you make

736
00:36:22,820 --> 00:36:24,620
are surely sold within three days

737
00:36:24,700 --> 00:36:25,820
whenever they’re exhibited

738
00:36:25,820 --> 00:36:27,340
in the Imperial Perfume Shop.

739
00:36:28,020 --> 00:36:30,340
Every time my brother’s wife comes,

740
00:36:30,700 --> 00:36:32,900
she asks for the solid perfume balls

741
00:36:33,100 --> 00:36:34,380
made by you.

742
00:36:36,980 --> 00:36:40,660
Tipsy Breeze solid perfume balls

743
00:36:41,060 --> 00:36:42,340
are the most popular in the capital,

744
00:36:43,100 --> 00:36:44,580
instead of Sweet Home?

745
00:36:47,740 --> 00:36:49,500
You are an emulative girl, Qiuhe.

746
00:36:54,380 --> 00:36:55,940
Cui Bai gave you a painting.

747
00:36:57,180 --> 00:36:58,780
I have it now.

748
00:37:00,220 --> 00:37:02,980
Wild geese are in the painting.

749
00:37:07,060 --> 00:37:08,620
As an imperial painter,

750
00:37:08,620 --> 00:37:10,420
he gave a painting to a maid without permission.

751
00:37:10,700 --> 00:37:12,020
It was somehow against the rules.

752
00:37:12,380 --> 00:37:14,340
But only because he adored you

753
00:37:14,420 --> 00:37:16,260
in the days when he painted you.

754
00:37:17,140 --> 00:37:18,620
He asked someone to give you the painting.

755
00:37:19,060 --> 00:37:20,660
That’s kind of romantic.

756
00:37:21,740 --> 00:37:23,420
Since I have the painting,

757
00:37:24,380 --> 00:37:25,700
I won’t let anyone else

758
00:37:25,700 --> 00:37:26,980
make an issue of it.

759
00:37:33,860 --> 00:37:34,820
But I want you

760
00:37:34,820 --> 00:37:35,820
to answer my question.

761
00:37:38,020 --> 00:37:40,940
Do you want to come into the real life

762
00:37:41,980 --> 00:37:44,780
and take care of the living thing with him?

763
00:37:46,540 --> 00:37:47,980
Or do you want to get separated from him

764
00:37:48,900 --> 00:37:50,420
by palace walls?

765
00:37:51,580 --> 00:37:52,860
He’s always out of the palace,

766
00:37:53,140 --> 00:37:54,340
while you’re always in.

767
00:37:55,100 --> 00:37:57,380
He can never see you clearly.

768
00:37:58,660 --> 00:38:00,420
You’ll always be as blurry as in the painting.

769
00:38:14,340 --> 00:38:16,300
Here, you’ll be lonely and desperate.

770
00:38:18,420 --> 00:38:20,140
But you’ll also have chances and honors.

771
00:38:21,820 --> 00:38:24,180
Chief Chu of Bureau of Clothing is often sick.

772
00:38:24,500 --> 00:38:25,900
She’ll leave after the new year.

773
00:38:26,980 --> 00:38:29,740
You have a better skill than Cai’er.

774
00:38:31,100 --> 00:38:32,300
But if you become

775
00:38:32,300 --> 00:38:34,140
the youngest chief of Bureau of Clothing,

776
00:38:34,700 --> 00:38:36,460
I don’t know when you can leave

777
00:38:37,580 --> 00:38:38,460
or if you can

778
00:38:39,380 --> 00:38:41,260
leave this place.

779
00:38:49,420 --> 00:38:50,140
Be careful. Don’t take it.

780
00:38:51,900 --> 00:38:52,780
Want to cheat, huh?

781
00:38:53,380 --> 00:38:54,500
Yes.

782
00:38:54,553 --> 00:38:55,380
Take this.

783
00:38:55,580 --> 00:38:56,380
Yaoyao.

784
00:38:57,700 --> 00:38:58,580
Yaoyao.

785
00:38:58,580 --> 00:38:59,740
Come. Let me hug you.

786
00:39:00,620 --> 00:39:01,700
Sorry, princess.

787
00:39:01,780 --> 00:39:03,140
Madam Zhang told us

788
00:39:03,140 --> 00:39:04,660
to protect the princess all the time

789
00:39:04,780 --> 00:39:06,260
and let no one get close to her.

790
00:39:10,780 --> 00:39:11,500
= Gao Taotao =
Forget it.

791
00:39:11,820 --> 00:39:12,500
You have your own little brother

792
00:39:12,500 --> 00:39:13,780
to play with.

793
00:39:14,020 --> 00:39:15,260
Why must you annoy others?

794
00:39:20,180 --> 00:39:20,900
Let’s go.

795
00:39:24,020 --> 00:39:25,540
How about this, Yaoyao?

796
00:39:25,740 --> 00:39:26,580
How about giving you

797
00:39:26,580 --> 00:39:27,580
some of my favorite toys

798
00:39:27,580 --> 00:39:28,460
for you to play with?

799
00:39:31,460 --> 00:39:32,300
Yaoyao.

800
00:39:33,260 --> 00:39:34,380
This bead is

801
00:39:34,380 --> 00:39:36,060
a new year present from father.

802
00:39:36,180 --> 00:39:37,660
This jade is from Her Highness.

803
00:39:37,820 --> 00:39:39,820
My mother embroidered the pouch for me.

804
00:39:39,940 --> 00:39:41,300
All are my favorite presents.

805
00:39:41,540 --> 00:39:42,380
Take them.

806
00:39:43,100 --> 00:39:43,860
Yaoyao.

807
00:39:46,620 --> 00:39:47,380
Stop!

808
00:40:05,020 --> 00:40:05,740
Madam.

809
00:40:05,820 --> 00:40:07,540
How many times have I told you to hold Yaoyao

810
00:40:07,540 --> 00:40:08,540
and let no one touch her?

811
00:40:08,980 --> 00:40:09,820
It’s been a while

812
00:40:09,820 --> 00:40:11,180
and you’re letting someone hurt her?

813
00:40:12,220 --> 00:40:12,940
But Princess Fukang

814
00:40:12,980 --> 00:40:13,980
insisted on hugging her.

815
00:40:14,620 --> 00:40:15,540
I refused.

816
00:40:15,780 --> 00:40:16,820
Then Princess Fukang

817
00:40:16,820 --> 00:40:18,220
wanted to give her some presents.

818
00:40:20,140 --> 00:40:20,900
Why?

819
00:40:21,420 --> 00:40:23,140
Why can’t you leave us alone?

820
00:40:23,620 --> 00:40:24,860
You got Chuyue dead.

821
00:40:24,860 --> 00:40:25,940
Now you’re going to kill Yaoyao.

822
00:40:26,220 --> 00:40:27,420
Again and again.

823
00:40:27,820 --> 00:40:29,100
What nonsense are you talking about?

824
00:40:29,820 --> 00:40:30,900
Yaoyao was suddenly ill.

825
00:40:30,900 --> 00:40:31,580
What’s happening in there?

826
00:40:31,580 --> 00:40:32,300
She was nearly suffocated.

827
00:40:32,820 --> 00:40:33,460
Your Majesty.

828
00:40:33,460 --> 00:40:34,660
She barely survived with the blessing.

829
00:40:34,820 --> 00:40:36,420
But you still don’t let her go.

830
00:40:37,220 --> 00:40:38,740
I’m going to unmask you

831
00:40:38,820 --> 00:40:40,580
and expose you evil heart.

832
00:40:41,060 --> 00:40:42,700
Stop! Stop!

833
00:40:42,700 --> 00:40:44,380
Madam Zhang. Madam Zhang.

834
00:40:44,380 --> 00:40:45,060
Let go of me!

835
00:40:45,060 --> 00:40:46,620
Your Majesty. Your Majesty.

836
00:40:46,660 --> 00:40:47,983
Don’t do that, madam.

837
00:40:49,460 --> 00:40:50,260
What are you doing?

838
00:40:52,620 --> 00:40:53,260
What’s happening?

839
00:40:53,820 --> 00:40:54,540
Your Majesty.

840
00:40:55,260 --> 00:40:56,660
Your Majesty, you know.

841
00:40:56,980 --> 00:40:58,260
When Yaoyao was ill,

842
00:40:58,540 --> 00:41:00,140
the physician said she had the asthma

843
00:41:00,140 --> 00:41:01,420
because of pollen or grass seeds.

844
00:41:01,780 --> 00:41:03,340
He had some doubt at that time.

845
00:41:03,980 --> 00:41:04,700
Yaoyao wasn’t even badly ill

846
00:41:04,700 --> 00:41:05,860
in spring.

847
00:41:06,260 --> 00:41:08,180
She shouldn’t have suffered in autumn.

848
00:41:09,100 --> 00:41:10,420
Then I wondered

849
00:41:10,860 --> 00:41:11,740
if anyone had

850
00:41:12,060 --> 00:41:14,060
poisoned Yaoyao’s clothes.

851
00:41:18,180 --> 00:41:20,580
Come. Stand up. Stand up.

852
00:41:24,420 --> 00:41:25,220
All right.

853
00:41:31,460 --> 00:41:32,220
Huirou.

854
00:41:34,780 --> 00:41:36,380
